import React from 'react';
import { Page, Text, View, Document, Font, Image } from '@react-pdf/renderer';
import { styles } from '../styles/resumeStyles';

Font.register({
  family: 'NanumGothic',
  src: 'https://fonts.gstatic.com/ea/nanumgothic/v5/NanumGothic-Regular.ttf'
});

const CheckBox = ({ checked }) => (
  <View style={styles.checkbox}>
    <Text>{checked ? '☑' : '☐'}</Text>
  </View>
);

const ResumeTemplate = ({ formData }) => {
  const CHECKED = '■';
  const UNCHECKED = '□';

  return (
    <Document>
      <Page size="A4" style={styles.page}>
        {/* 서식 번호 */}
        <View style={styles.header}>
          <Text style={styles.formNumber}>[서식 1-11호] 노인일자리 참여신청서(참여노인용)</Text>
        </View>

        <Text style={styles.title}>노인일자리 참여신청서(참여노인용)</Text>
        <Text style={styles.subTitle}>(앞면)</Text>

        <View style={styles.table}>
          {/* 첫 번째 행: 사진, 성명, 전화번호 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <View style={styles.photoCell}>
              <Text>사진</Text>
              {formData.photo && (
                <Image source={formData.photo} />
              )}
            </View>
            <View style={styles.nameCell}>
              <View style={styles.nameRow}>
                <Text>성명</Text>
                <Text>{formData.name}</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.nameRow}>
                <Text>주민등록번호</Text>
                <Text>{formData.residentNumber1}-{formData.residentNumber2} (만 세)</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.nameRow}>
                <Text>주소</Text>
                <Text>{formData.address}</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.phoneCell}>
              <Text>전화번호</Text>
              <Text>자택: {formData.homePhone}</Text>
              <Text>휴대폰: {formData.mobilePhone}</Text>
              <Text>가족연락처: {formData.familyPhone}</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 최종학력 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>최종학력</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              {['무학', '초졸', '중졸', '고졸', '전문대졸', '대졸이상'].map(edu => (
                <Text key={edu}>
                  {formData.education === edu ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} {edu}
                </Text>
              ))}
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 세대구성 형태 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>세대구성 형태</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              <Text>{formData.householdType === '독신' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 독신</Text>
              <Text>{formData.householdType === '가족동거(노부모,손자녀,장애인)' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 가족동거(노부모,손자녀,장애인)</Text>
              <Text>{formData.householdType === '가족동거(경제능력가족)' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 가족동거(경제능력가족)</Text>
              <Text>{formData.householdType === '노인부부' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 노인부부</Text>
              <Text>{formData.householdType === '기타' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 기타</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 동거가족 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>동거가족</Text>
            <View style={styles.value}>
              <Text>동거가족: </Text>
              <CheckBox checked={!formData.spouse && !formData.children && !formData.grandchildren} />
              <Text>없음 </Text>
              <CheckBox checked={formData.spouse || formData.children || formData.grandchildren} />
              <Text>있음</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 일자리사업 참여경력 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>일자리사업 참여경력</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              <Text>일자리사업 참여경력: </Text>
              <CheckBox checked={!formData.workExperience.isNew} />
              <Text>금년도 신규참여 </Text>
              <CheckBox checked={formData.workExperience.isNew} />
              <Text>참여경력 있음</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 기초생활수급권자 해당유무 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>기초생활수급권자{'\n'}해당유무</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              <Text>{formData.basicLivingRecipient === '해당' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 해당</Text>
              <Text>{formData.basicLivingRecipient === '비해당' ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 비해당 (의료급여 수급권자 2종 포함)</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 경제정도 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>경제정도</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              {['매우좋음', '좋음', '보통', '나쁨', '매우나쁨'].map(status => (
                <Text key={status}>
                  {formData.economicStatus === status ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} {status}
                </Text>
              ))}
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 주거형태 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>주거형태</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              {['자택', '전세', '월세', '기타'].map(type => (
                <Text key={type}>
                  {formData.housingType === type ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} {type}
                </Text>
              ))}
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 건강상태 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>건강상태</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              {['매우건강', '건강', '보통', '나쁨', '매우나쁨'].map(status => (
                <Text key={status}>
                  {formData.healthStatus === status ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} {status}
                </Text>
              ))}
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 참여희망사업 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>참여희망사업</Text>
            <View style={styles.threeColumns}>
              <View style={styles.column}>
                <Text>①{formData.desiredPrograms.first}</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.column}>
                <Text>②{formData.desiredPrograms.second}</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.lastColumn}>
                <Text>③{formData.desiredPrograms.third}</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 신청동기 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>신청동기</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              {['경제적도움', '자기발전', '사회참여', '시간활용', '건강증진', '기타'].map(motive => (
                <Text key={motive}>
                  {formData.applicationMotives.includes(motive) ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} {motive}
                </Text>
              ))}
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 전년도사업 자원봉사참여유무 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>전년도사업{'\n'}자원봉사참여유무</Text>
            <View style={styles.value}>
              <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
                <Text>{formData.volunteerWork.participated ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 유</Text>
                <Text>{!formData.volunteerWork.participated ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 무</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
                <Text>건강보험 직장가입자: </Text>
                <CheckBox checked={formData.volunteerWork.healthInsurance === 'false'} />
                <Text>비해당 </Text>
                <CheckBox checked={formData.volunteerWork.healthInsurance === 'true'} />
                <Text>해당</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 기초노령연금 수급유무 */}
          <View style={styles.row}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>기초노령연금{'\n'}수급 유무</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              <Text>{formData.basicPensionStatus.receiving ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 유 (기초노령연금액 {formData.basicPensionStatus.amount}만원)</Text>
              <Text>{!formData.basicPensionStatus.receiving ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 무</Text>
            </View>
          </View>

          {/* 장기요양 등급판정여부 */}
          <View style={styles.lastRow}>
            <Text style={styles.label}>장기요양{'\n'}등급판정여부</Text>
            <View style={styles.checkboxRow}>
              <Text>{formData.longTermCare.status ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 유</Text>
              <Text>{!formData.longTermCare.status ? CHECKED : UNCHECKED} 무</Text>
            </View>
          </View>
        </View>
      </Page>
    </Document>
  );
};

export default ResumeTemplate;
